Introduction

Keiju is a Japanese singer and dancer under JYP Entertainment. He is best known as a member of the boy group KickFlip.

He participated in the SBS survival program Loud, which led to him becoming a pre-debut member of the boy group JYPE LOUD. On January 6, 2025, he was officially revealed as a member of the boy group KickFlip.
